  * work on fixing coverity scan results:
    - fix some off-by-one errors
    - fix some resource leaks
    - fixes in chroot() handling
    - fix some missing va_end()
  * make the code -Wall clean again
  * remove duplicated #include<list>
  * add .travis.yml
