  * apt-pkg/acquire-item.cc:
    - fix a merge mistake that prevents the fallback to the 
      uncompressed 'Packages' to work correctly (closes: #409284)

 -- Michael Vogt <mvo@debian.org>  Wed, 29 Oct 2008 09:36:24 +0100

