    Closes: #100590
  * Lame LD_LIBRARY_PATH thing. Closes: #98928
  * apt-cache search searchs provide names too now. Closes: #98695
  * Checksum and long lines problem. Closes: #106591
  * .aptignr and empty files are just a warning. Closes: #97364

